art Appliances, Hindware Atlantic, and FGV By Hindware brand name. The company was formerly known as Somany Home Innovation Limited and changed its name to Hindware Home Innovation Limited in May 2022. Hindware Home Innovation Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Gurugram, India."}}